          { "name": "phone", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.phone}}" },
          { "name": "interest", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.interest}}" },
          { "name": "prepared_at", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.prepared_at}}" },
          { "name": "candidate_path", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.candidate_path}}" },
          { "name": "has_workflow_output", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.has_workflow_output}}" },
          { "name": "has_output", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.has_output}}" },
          { "name": "has_data", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.has_data}}" },
          { "name": "has_values", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.has_values}}" },
          { "name": "debug_candidate_json", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.debug_candidate_json}}" },
          { "name": "debug_payload_json", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.debug_payload_json}}" },
          { "name": "received_at", "value": "{{node_normalize_submission.received_at}}" }
        ]
      },
      "position": { "x": 1140, "y": 320 },
      "is_disabled": false
    },
    {
      "node_id": "note_overview",
      "type": "note",
      "name": "HTML Page Test Guide",
      "description": "",
      "parameters": {
        "noteText": "HTML PAGE TEST\n\nPurpose:\nTest the new html_page node without writing to the database or contacting anyone.\n\nSafe test:\n1. Start the workflow manually.\n2. Confirm execution pauses at Open Test Lead Page.\n3. Enter sample values or click Load Sample Data.\n4. Click Apply Output.\n5. Close the page to continue the workflow.\n6. Inspect Normalize Page Output and Done: HTML Page Closed.\n7. Check candidate_path, debug_candidate_json, and debug_payload_json to see the exact downstream payload shape.\n\nExpected routing:\nStart -> HTML Page -> Normalize Output -> Done.\n\nRuntime note:\n- The page receives prior payload in window.workflowInput.\n- The page sends values forward through window.workflowOutput.\n- The workflow resumes through the normal output handle when the page is closed.\n\nNo database, email, webhook, or customer side effects occur."
      },
      "position": { "x": 180, "y": -120 },
      "is_disabled": false
    }
  ],
